Get started with FuzzyRecord

1) Create a vhost in your chosen webserver, pointing at the htdocs folder. Apache example:

<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerAdmin ben@allseeing-i.com
    DocumentRoot "/Users/ben/Sites/FuzzyRecord/htdocs"
    ServerName fuzzytest
</VirtualHost>

2) Copy config/config.default.php to config/config.php and point it at your database

Documentation is available at:

http://allseeing-i.com/FuzzyRecord